<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Feliz cumpleaños</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg1: #02030a;
      --bg2: #070b1d;
      --bg3: #0c1230;
      --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
      --glass-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
      --text: #ffffff;
      --accent: #ffd86b;
      --paper: rgba(250, 250, 255, 0.94);
      --paper-text: #1a1b33;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      overflow: hidden;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 20%, rgba(125, 90, 255, 0.28), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 28%, rgba(255, 95, 175, 0.18), transparent 16%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 72%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.12), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg1) 0%, var(--bg2) 50%, #010207 100%);
    }

    .space,
    .space::before,
    .space::after {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      content: "";
    }

    .space {
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 10% 18%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 22% 64%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 35% 30%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 52% 14%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 68% 44%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 84% 22%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(1px 1px at 90% 70%, #fff 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(2px 2px at 60% 28%, rgba(255,255,255,.85) 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(2px 2px at 78% 16%, rgba(255,255,255,.75) 99%, transparent 100%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,.08), transparent 38%);
      animation: drift 20s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .space::before {
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 16% 64%, rgba(130, 70, 255, 0.30), transparent 9%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 72% 24%, rgba(0, 195, 255, 0.22), transparent 11%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 54% 48%, rgba(255, 100, 180, 0.18), transparent 12%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 84% 58%, rgba(255, 214, 107, 0.10), transparent 8%);
      filter: blur(18px);
      animation: glow 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .space::after {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 42%, rgba(255,255,255,.08) 50%, transparent 58%);
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      animation: sweep 14s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes drift {
      from { transform: translateY(0); }
      to { transform: translateY(-40px); }
    }

    @keyframes glow {
      from { opacity: 0.55; transform: scale(1); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.08); }
    }

    @keyframes sweep {
      from { transform: translateX(-100%); }
      to { transform: translateX(100%); }
    }

    .wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: 100%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: "Great Vibes", cursive;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-shadow:
        0 0 18px rgba(255,255,255,.28),
        0 0 42px rgba(255,165,255,.22);
    }

    .subtitle {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto 26px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }

    .open-btn {
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 4.2rem;
      line-height: 1;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(255,255,255,.30));
      transition: transform .18s ease, filter .18s ease;
    }

    .open-btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.08) translateY(-2px);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,.45));
    }

    .open-btn:focus-visible,
    .close:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid #fff;
      outline-offset: 4px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .hint {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: .92rem;
      opacity: .8;
    }

    .modal {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(1, 3, 10, 0.74);
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 18px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .modal.show {
      display: flex;
    }

    .letter {
      width: min(760px, 95vw);
      max-height: 86vh;
      overflow: auto;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.16), rgba(255,255,255,.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .letter h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .paper {
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--paper-text);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 22px 20px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    }

    .paper p {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .close {
      margin-top: 16px;
      border: 0;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .close:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.20);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.9rem, 16vw, 5rem);
      }

      .open-btn {
        font-size: 3.6rem;
      }

      .letter {
        padding: 20px 16px;
      }

      .paper {
        padding: 18px 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="space"></div>

  <main class="wrap">
    <div>
      <h1>Feliz cumpleaños</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">Toca la cartica para abrir el mensaje especial.</div>
      <button class="open-btn" id="open" aria-label="Abrir carta">✉️</button>
      <div class="hint">Carta interactiva</div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <div class="modal" id="modal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="letter" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="title">
      <h2 id="title">Tu carta</h2>
      <div class="paper">
        <p>Querido/a [Nombre]:</p>
        <p>
          Hoy celebramos tu vida, tu alegría y todo lo bonito que transmites.
          Espero que este cumpleaños te regale sonrisas sinceras, abrazos sinceros
          y momentos que queden para siempre en tu corazón.
        </p>
        <p>
          Que este nuevo año te acerque a tus sueños, te llene de paz y te recuerde
          lo valioso/a que eres para quienes te quieren.
        </p>
        <p>¡Feliz cumpleaños! Con cariño, Nicolás.</p>
      </div>
      <button class="close" id="close">Cerrar</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const openBtn = document.getElementById("open");
    const modal = document.getElementById("modal");
    const closeBtn = document.getElementById("close");

    openBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
      modal.classList.add("show");
      modal.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "false");
      closeBtn.focus();
    });

    closeBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
      modal.classList.remove("show");
      modal.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
      openBtn.focus();
    });

    modal.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
      if (e.target === modal) closeBtn.click();
    });

    document.addEventListener("keydown", (e) => {
      if (e.key === "Escape") closeBtn.click();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
